       "5 Mandelbrot Qud : sqr(z)+(0.2*z^3)+z+z+c""6 Flattop : (z-0.2)^2 + (c*z)/(z-0.1)" "7 Funny : (z+z)*c-z^2""8 Funny : z^2*z+c" \
